{"tid":2211374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美國財政部文件：客戶進行「龐氏騙局」但滙控仍容許有問題款項由美國轉帳至香港","createTime":"2020-09-21T05:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T08:29:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":84,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"766ccaed7f5429cac6e89564c4cac0c78c339ed2","tid":2211374,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"國際調查記者聯盟披露美國財政部文件，顯示2000年至2017年期間，銀行等向當局提交的可疑活動報告，涉及兩萬億美元交易。<br />\n<br />\n其中，有關滙控的文件指出，滙控2013年9月已收到監管部門通知，有客戶涉嫌以講座推銷投資等進行「龐氏騙局」，但仍然容許有問題款項由美國轉帳至香港，涉資約8000萬美元。直至2014年4月有關人士被起訴，滙控才取消涉及的香港戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/finance/5f68342734b0310f74e7f354/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E6%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%97%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E5%AF%A6%E9%AB%94%E6%B8%85%E5%96%AE-%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%B7%A8%E9%A1%8D%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%AC%BE%E9%A0%85%E8%BD%89%E5%B8%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ffinance%2F5f68342734b0310f74e7f354%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25BB%2599%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%259D%25A0%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%2596%25AE-%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E9%25A1%258D%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%25A0%2585%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%25B8%25B3&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=26c8acd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/finance/5f68342734b0310f74e7f354/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E6%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%97%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E5%AF%A6%E9%AB%94%E6%B8%85%E5%96%AE-%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%B7%A8%E9%A1%8D%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%AC%BE%E9%A0%85%E8%BD%89%E5%B8%B3</a>"},{"pid":"61164b55e32958399871f7dd29ea85fe4b1ace28","tid":2211374,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite